request.description:
This endpoint retrieves all existing zoo species

### Request

No request body is required for this endpoint.

```
GET /api/v1/species

 ```

### Response

The response will be a JSON object with the following schema:

``` json
[  
 {
    "id": "number",
    "zone": {
            "id": "number",
            "name": "string"
        },
    "name": "string"
  },
  {
    "id": "number",
    "zone": {
            "id": "number",
            "name": "string"
        },
    "name": "string"
  }
]

 ```

#### Example

##### Request

```
GET /api/v1/species

 ```

##### Response

``` json
[
    {
        "id": 1,
        "zone": {
            "id": 1,
            "name": "Anfibios"
        },
        "name": "rana"
    },
    {
        "id": 2,
        "zone": {
            "id": 1,
            "name": "Anfibios"
        },
        "name": "Salamandra"
    }
]

 ```

